title: DSW Style Transparent Chair Moss Grey/Light Wood
body: A classic piece from Charles Eames for more than 60 years style by Mobelaris. This unbeatable chair design is becoming more popular than ever. This Mobelaris style of DSW Transparent Chair is a contemporary version of the legendary fiberglass chair. The DSW has become an icon in many interiors in its own way. An easy to keep clean and lightweight chair that is rich in character.
